Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是記錄媒體的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.34,0:00:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是舊式的 但應該沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以復原嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許其中記錄著我們沒有見過的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:00:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 可以了！
Comment: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前不是說過會帶我參觀加爾剛蒂亞的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰說過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近哥很忙 沒這個閒工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 怎麼這麼說話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都在火海中和我互許終生了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,許個頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 和你這種野蠻潑辣的妹子比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫柔端莊的小姐更是我的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:02:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著 拆除之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 映出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我們的機器還是第一次讀出如此詳細的數據呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是設計圖 或者是操縱手冊嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人形機器人不同嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以技術水平來看 這東西和Chamber更為接近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥機器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製作這東西的人們走向了宇宙 並最終構築了銀河同盟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便離開了凍結的地球 他們仍舊沒有放棄鬥爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然可悲 但這確實是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:04:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們必須從中吸取教訓 避免重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃午飯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到庫蓋爾艦團上也有這麼棒的店舖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能消停點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這些料理加爾剛蒂亞上可都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也沒有點這麼多的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會負責吃光的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？啊…是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出遠門的時候我都會坐這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪真的很喜歡機械之類的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮尼歐都想把她挖走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 真假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候是情不自禁…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還去看了Chamber的駕駛艙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候…也是情不自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還開著潛水人形機器人去救雷德了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…別再說這個話題了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是大家太搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的菜過會兒呈上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好吃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再來！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還打算吃那麼多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒辦法跑來跑去和長時間運動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我天生心臟就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也沒法治療 所以我只能去適應它了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有姐姐陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有醫生 雷德和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真堅強呢 貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你也很堅強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 你在一個陌生的地方開始了生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻像這樣交到了朋友 工作著 活著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很弱小 但卻都很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 莉瑪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說要先回一趟自己的船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是想要洗衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟今天天氣很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也回去洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊抓捕對象 把他帶走就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過了 我們的目的是讓雷德協助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾到底有多大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能否駕馭這股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題還有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不弄清楚 就無法將它用於戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的知識對我們而言是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用強只會適得其反
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已在捕獲Striker駕駛員的行動中失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本國應該已經很不耐煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員的死亡是計劃之外的事態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相比之下 應該認為新對象的出現是一個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得想辦法讓雷德自己離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的方針不變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果本國翻臉就玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不單單是我們 就連這機體也保不住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你報告一下目前的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居民們似乎相當勞累
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為接收的前庫蓋爾艦團人員安排居住地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和維修船隻的工作還在繼續進行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物資不足這點也很讓人擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前幾天雖然從商船那裡補充了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因為人員增加 所以消費也很快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用光只是時間問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零件和電池都搞不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各個公會都很頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦團長 希望你能採取一些對策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個地方 短缺的用品應該都可以得到補充
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說休閒設施也都很完善
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮城…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是艦團長莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一件事需要向大家宣佈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始 加爾剛蒂亞將前往海上貨易據點 通稱龍宮城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 龍宮城是什麼地方啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請各船主們及各公會制定好物資採購計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時 我們也充分考慮了居民的慰勞問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是龍宮城！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大規模的設施竟然能漂浮在海面上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 好多海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅露蒂 紗雅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是第一次這麼近距離看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 玩個痛快吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝貝爾沒辦法來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這麼大的地方逛來逛去 對他的身體負擔太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他說去幫奧爾德姆醫生調查東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給他買點禮物回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝各位提交計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會據此來進行貿易談判的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從同行那裡聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這裡鐵之類的物資好像全都漲價了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蔬菜種子和穀物好像也都被買斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說 我們出售的東西也可以賣個好價錢嘍？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之就是行情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就乘機賺上一筆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 為什麼是這個時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎和陸地的動向有關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和陸地有關？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詳情還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可以確定的是有部分物資流向了陸地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要時刻關注陸地各國的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許他們接下來會有新的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和龍宮城高層見面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會旁敲側擊一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 陸地嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相當可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們該怎麼辦 頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然對這遊樂園沒啥興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但調查一下也沒什麼壞處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去做準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直像祭典一樣呢 莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 要試試看那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個去打想要的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個 像這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑一個喜歡的打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 你太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是故意沒裝子彈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海豚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 有好多的海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海洋哺乳動物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經離開海洋 後來又回到海中生活的物種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要選擇這樣的進化之路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到海中的牠們 現在到底在追求什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像可以和海豚一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和海豚…一起玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳裝都準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳裝是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啦 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米也準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿內衣不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼先去購物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件很適合莉瑪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 不錯 不錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 這件如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面也有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海豚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人羨慕嫉妒恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是覺得艾米他們真要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這麼開心的事我從來都沒有經歷過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟你在那個庫蓋爾艦團嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼心事就和我們說說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們是同伴也是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在想 要是能像那樣和哥哥一起玩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原來有哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在艦團上嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長得帥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們所需要的物資 我們應該都能夠提供
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大艦團加爾剛蒂亞能停泊敝城 我們也是與有榮焉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們出售的商品也十分豐富 可以說是一次互惠互利的貿易
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部分物資的流動存在偏向的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來只是我杞人憂天 這下心裡就踏實了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的消息還真是靈通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我們而言 每一位客戶都很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是不會厚此薄彼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最新的世界地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面也標記了各勢力的分佈情況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我們表示友好的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知幾位之後是否方便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請務必接受我們的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個好像不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著就像能做出各種各樣的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就選這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦 你們都在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少見啊 你們會來這種店舖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,品味不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在給貝貝爾買禮物 正打算回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子們就老老實實地回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是大人的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人的時間算什麼玩意兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是敢敗壞風氣 我可不會輕饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉吉特船長…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了防止居民給龍宮城添麻煩 我正在看守！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊…喝多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰讓她喝的啊！這樣子簡直太糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我們要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就兩個大老粗去？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧你說的 當然是現找一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 可以還給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛剛奪走的我的那顆心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這樣兒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 莉瑪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本國那邊已經開始做回收準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在部隊到達之前沒有達成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行動就會被終止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 他們打算把馬茲爾也捨棄掉嗎？這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最高機密的兵器不能再這樣放置於國外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面應該是這樣想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們最害怕的就是情報被洩露給敵國了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我想辦法壓下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一會兒就行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機械自行解析並運用語言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是遺失的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會說話的機器…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像Chamber那樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是像他那樣的人工智能的前身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然連這種東西都造出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不更深入地和人類交流 就無法度過嚴酷的冰河期
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這麼一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡有什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人形機器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是那個設計圖裡的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 我希望你能來我的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫助我研究這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:49.94,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,檢測到了生命體反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾 我可能會讓你置身險境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:58.67,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,影像記錄中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 還是不可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:05.74,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,影像記錄中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我無法理解你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我開動了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.91,0:22:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有這一條路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的我卻開始討厭戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了？要單獨和我談
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:22:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:22:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事想要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能幫我說服雷德 讓他離開加爾剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.83,0:23:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我不懂 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然還有艾米和貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我聽不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好解釋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.59,0:23:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望雷德 艾米和貝貝爾跟我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去哪…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去我出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸地？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.12,0:23:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？莉瑪你是陸地人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.71,0:23:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果艾米來的話 雷德肯定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.03,0:23:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他沒有回答
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.60,0:23:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定是覺得不能丟下你不管
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這麼覺得的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.76,0:23:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.52,0:23:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能離開加爾剛蒂亞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:23:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝貝爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸地上也許有辦法治好貝貝爾的病
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.63,0:24:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.03,0:24:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次見到陸地上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.79,0:24:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人告訴過我 不要和陸地人有所瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.79,0:24:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到莉瑪是陸地人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.16,0:24:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使她說讓我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.11,0:24:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是移居到陌生的地方這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.39,0:24:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果能治好貝貝爾 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.28,0:24:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果治不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.36,0:24:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會讓那孩子陷入危險之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.94,0:24:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.97,0:24:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然變成了這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.22,0:24:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道該怎麼辦啊 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.95,0:25:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦團長
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.26,0:25:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4點鐘方向有艦團正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.58,0:25:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續保持警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.06,0:25:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.98,0:25:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從來沒有見過的船影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.78,0:25:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海賊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.70,0:25:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.38,0:26:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓護衛艦出動
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.16,0:26:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.12,0:26:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.26,0:26:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒趕上嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.47,0:26:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終究還是打算來硬的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.56,0:26:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不通知我們一聲就現身
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.01,0:26:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明已經把我們連同行動一起放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.96,0:26:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.89,0:26:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.43,0:26:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要抓到雷德 就是我們說的算了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.94,0:26:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捨棄掉莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.13,0:26:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們出發
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.92,0:26:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告接近中的艦團
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.59,0:26:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是加爾剛蒂亞艦團
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.61,0:26:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告知貴艦團的所屬以及行動目的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.34,0:26:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦團長 那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.22,0:26:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好像不是海賊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.34,0:27:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛開始就一直以現在的距離和我們並行
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.83,0:27:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦團長
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.42,0:27:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.30,0:27:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的警戒對象都沒有裝備連接器
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.50,0:27:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥用的船隻…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.00,0:27:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝羅茲 這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.76,0:27:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.85,0:27:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.01,0:27:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪 你知道什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.41,0:27:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在接近的艦團到底是什麼來歷？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.25,0:27:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是從陸地而來的特務艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.02,0:27:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸地？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.96,0:27:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.36,0:27:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前說過 陸地上也許能治好貝貝爾的病
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.75,0:27:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也會被迫過上比疾病更痛苦的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.68,0:27:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.87,0:27:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我隱瞞了這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.89,0:27:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.10,0:27:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是卡奇納斯號
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.14,0:27:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.34,0:27:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.83,0:27:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米被抓走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.50,0:27:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.36,0:27:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.68,0:27:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被突然出現的兩個男人抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.50,0:27:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然自作主張！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.48,0:27:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.81,0:27:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地點在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.57,0:28:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在之前去過的那家食堂附近
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.49,0:28:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上趕過去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.43,0:28:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.39,0:28:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩個人是我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.22,0:28:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的目標是你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.48,0:28:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.62,0:28:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米是人質
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.81,0:28:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你被抓的話就無法回到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.89,0:28:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去說服他們把艾米帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.96,0:28:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.22,0:28:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.11,0:28:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄刻阿諾斯號 緊急聯絡！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.11,0:28:21.05,ruby,NTP,0,300,0,,Oceanus
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.11,0:28:21.05,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：希臘神話中大洋河的河神
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.71,0:28:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米被抓走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.10,0:28:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.68,0:28:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個有精神的小姑娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.62,0:28:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.00,0:28:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻釋放人質！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.62,0:28:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.15,0:28:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她現在可是我們的生命線
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.91,0:28:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果以這女孩的生命為籌碼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.27,0:29:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對象就會幫忙幫到底的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.15,0:29:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.57,0:29:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然特務艦隊已經現身
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.75,0:29:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就說明一切都遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.59,0:29:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計劃已經被放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.05,0:29:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們怎麼就是不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.25,0:29:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們和你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.58,0:29:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只管完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.58,0:29:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.33,0:29:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.85,0:29:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.37,0:29:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西果然不是人形機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.38,0:29:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪 這到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.62,0:29:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們稱他為強化外裝
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.62,0:29:54.21,ruby,NTP,250,0,0,,Augmented body
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.82,0:29:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫馬茲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.60,0:29:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的同伴在駕駛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.06,0:29:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.75,0:30:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.00,0:30:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是同伴 是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.15,0:30:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是無人機
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.68,0:30:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.60,0:30:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.90,0:30:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對面來電
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.41,0:30:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本艦隊的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.21,0:30:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是殲滅正在脫離貴艦團的船舶 人員以及裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.90,0:30:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該船舶屬於我國
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.06,0:30:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望貴艦團不要進行妨礙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.10,0:30:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法認可
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.77,0:30:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩船上都確認到了本艦團的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.24,0:30:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請終止攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.08,0:30:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我國的正當權利 貴艦團已處在我軍的艦炮射程內
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.63,0:30:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.77,0:30:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴艦團的阻撓行為 我們將以武力加以排除
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.63,0:30:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦團長
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.02,0:30:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 不能放任居民的安全受到威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.11,0:31:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全艦做好攻擊準備 強化警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.15,0:31:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,護衛艦請開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.11,0:31:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 乘上來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.56,0:31:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了艾米 我無論如何都必須保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.13,0:31:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.37,0:31:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.33,0:31:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾想把你捲進陸地上已經歷時幾百年的國與國的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.59,0:31:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了獲取勝利 我曾想利用你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.49,0:31:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在我已經做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.39,0:31:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有權利破壞你們的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.97,0:31:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.46,0:31:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快乘上來！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.34,0:32:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非戰鬥人員請撤到艦團左舷！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.66,0:32:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重複 非戰鬥人員請撤到艦團左舷！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.26,0:32:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別推我！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.60,0:32:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別推！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.76,0:32:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.15,0:32:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人不在我們的射程內
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.50,0:32:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邊推進邊警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.02,0:32:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認到敵人大型艦開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.80,0:32:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各護衛艦 做好迎擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.16,0:32:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認兩側交差著彈
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.51,0:32:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離已經被對方測量到了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.06,0:32:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.26,0:32:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.91,0:32:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,護衛艦允許應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.63,0:33:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.21,0:33:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.52,0:33:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.78,0:33:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去避難！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.60,0:33:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.11,0:33:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.12,0:33:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.12,0:33:34.38,ruby,NTP,0,180,0,,Adios
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.94,0:33:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會忘記你的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.56,0:33:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.50,0:33:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.76,0:33:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.00,0:33:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集情報辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.85,0:33:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜此所賜 我下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.48,0:34:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.42,0:34:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.91,0:34:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.08,0:34:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從來沒見過這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.53,0:34:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西正在擴張控制系統嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.15,0:34:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.74,0:34:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.19,0:34:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前從來沒發生過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.06,0:34:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能開得動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.55,0:34:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.98,0:34:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像他的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.32,0:34:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.07,0:34:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在腦海裡描繪出你想做的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.98,0:34:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你想讓這傢伙做的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.52,0:34:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這東西的機制和Chamber一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.45,0:34:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他應該能領會的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.95,0:35:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛到那個地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.03,0:36:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凱奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.57,0:36:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保鏢工作關門大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.45,0:36:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去做海賊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.23,0:36:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在不想和陸地那邊扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.26,0:36:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 唯有這次不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.99,0:36:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬧個痛快 就當是離艦聲明了！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.43,0:36:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.06,0:36:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別停歇！繼續開炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.43,0:36:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電磁兵器？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.74,0:37:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.70,0:37:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.17,0:37:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.39,0:37:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.60,0:37:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.43,0:37:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.28,0:37:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.45,0:37:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.51,0:37:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.17,0:37:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.27,0:37:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝著我來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.28,0:37:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著機體還沒有流入他國 就先沉在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.93,0:37:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.03,0:37:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米…平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.47,0:37:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得趕緊離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.03,0:38:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.76,0:38:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在駕駛那東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.70,0:38:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.21,0:38:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然沒辦法像雷德那麼順手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.40,0:38:22.94,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,確認到操作機能顯著下降 請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.73,0:38:31.81,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.57,0:38:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是這樣嗎？還是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.73,0:38:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.60,0:39:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣或許也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.36,0:39:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是部了不起的機械
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.60,0:39:54.41,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,已確認搭乘者的生體情報以及機體的損壞狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.15,0:39:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果很多部像你這樣的機械都能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.63,0:40:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切就都會亂套
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.99,0:40:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說是戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.50,0:40:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連生存之地都會毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.67,0:40:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 我應該早點讓你回歸海底的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.90,0:40:15.84,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,將搭乘者認定為專屬駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.31,0:40:23.15,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,將機能維持更新為最優先事項
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.71,0:40:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.84,0:40:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.21,0:41:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.65,0:41:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾…Sys…tem
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…說話…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.34,0:41:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是操作界面
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.50,0:41:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.60,0:42:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是馬茲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.37,0:42:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.97,0:42:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.10,0:42:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.56,0:42:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.65,0:42:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.58,0:42:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.56,0:42:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！你要做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.17,0:42:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.04,0:42:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 等一下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.66,0:42:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬茲爾!!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.27,0:43:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.87,0:43:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.69,0:43:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.88,0:43:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.68,0:43:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪 太好了 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.08,0:43:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在那裡別動 我現在就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.17,0:43:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我已經不能回到加爾剛蒂亞了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.85,0:43:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.77,0:43:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情變成這樣 都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.94,0:43:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個過錯是不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.91,0:43:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟這些沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.11,0:43:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就別管這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.36,0:44:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我而言 馬茲爾就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.78,0:44:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.98,0:44:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經沒有回去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.37,0:44:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你很困擾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.90,0:44:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得得救了 你卻不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.50,0:44:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凱奇 快帶莉瑪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.93,0:44:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要就此告辭 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.84,0:44:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凱奇…誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.68,0:44:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那眼神 就像活著本身就已經是對你的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.09,0:44:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.30,0:44:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.64,0:44:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有接受這份罪行的覺悟的話
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.39,0:45:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.00,0:45:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請允許我用這種方法贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.48,0:45:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.68,0:45:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.39,0:45:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為海洋只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.82,0:45:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.50,0:45:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 長期以來的修復工作真是辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.40,0:46:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻 加爾剛蒂亞又增加了一個新的生活據點
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.45,0:46:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛我們所遭遇的身份不明的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.64,0:46:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是陸地國家所擁有的海上力量
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.72,0:46:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧護衛艦的奮鬥以及各位的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.58,0:46:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使得受害情況縮減到了最低
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.82,0:46:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎來了新的船隻之後
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.05,0:46:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加爾剛蒂亞今後也必須是一個和平昌盛的艦團
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.90,0:46:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此 請各位助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.91,0:46:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架機體確實和這東西連接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.98,0:46:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這地球上還有我所不知道的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.72,0:46:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.40,0:46:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪出生在戰爭連連的陸地上
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.53,0:46:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是怎樣生活下來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.21,0:46:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是懷著怎樣的心情看待我們的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.57,0:47:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.11,0:47:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.27,0:47:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉瑪告訴過我 她不想破壞我們的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.68,0:47:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管遇到怎樣的困難
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.88,0:47:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都要在這裡生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.01,0:47:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會在這裡保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.50,0:47:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德
