Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:53.95,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}まわるよ まわるよ 世界はまわるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:56.97,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}心の羽根ひろげ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:02:01.80,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}僕らは今日を生きていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:06.89,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}たとえどんな風が吹いても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:11.07,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}何度でも自由を求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:16.05,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}はばたいていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:20.41,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}悲しみを乗り越えた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:25.43,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}光があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:09.66,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}將聚散離合深埋心間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:16.54,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏出前進的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.96,0:01:23.68,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}記憶總以柔和的觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:28.22,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}對我們報以微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:32.30,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}天空的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:35.46,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}與濤聲的歌謠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:41.74,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}自然而然的幸福滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:46.42,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我們找到了開始的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:53.95,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}日出日落 冬去春來 世界不斷變遷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:56.97,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我們張開心的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:02:01.80,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}度過一天又一天的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:06.89,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}無論面對怎樣的風向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:11.07,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始終朝著自由的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:16.05,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}振翅飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:20.41,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因為那悲傷的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:25.43,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}存在著綻放的光芒
